{"tid":533917,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"曾志偉告毀謗, 教母態度變軟「少說話」","createTime":"2018-01-19T09:51:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-19T10:58:06.000Z","uid":134071,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"1ef22f6372626fdc99efe7576e87baf11bf29775","tid":533917,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T09:51:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://ent.ltn.com.tw/news/breakingnews/2316774\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fent.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fbreakingnews%2F2316774&d=O%2FDIUHGNus3%2BZXxg%2BPUTdRxs2jlPaATBKfveiEY0UFo%3D&h=9e7149cc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fent.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fbreakingnews%2F2316774&h=470090c5\" target=\"_blank\">http://ent.ltn.com.tw/news/breakingnews/2316774</a><br />\n<br />\n曾志偉硬起來告毀謗 教母態度變軟「少說話」<br />\n2018/01/19 13:12 <br />\n〔記者翁子涵／台北報導〕64歲港星曾志偉日前被中國媒體爆多年前曾染指女星藍潔瑛，「金牌模特兒教母」韓穎華又狂轟他「不止一次性侵女藝人」，曾志偉2天前怒開記者會駁斥謠言，不過韓穎華沒在怕，接連在微博嗆「賤人」、「實在有這檔子的事」，對此，曾志偉今硬起來，正式提出訴狀，告她毀謗。<br />\n<br />\n據港媒報導，曾志偉昨向香港高等法院提出訴狀，控告韓穎華毀謗，指控她的言論流傳香港以至全世界，不僅讓他名譽受損，還得承受壓力及尷尬，要求法庭下令禁止韓穎華再發表相關言論，並要求賠償及道歉。<br />\n<br />\n對此，韓穎華態度轉趨低調發文表示，會在律師建議下「少說話」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/19/175108_d0ad786e1d55f0b7767e85c5776f8eef.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F19%2F175108_d0ad786e1d55f0b7767e85c5776f8eef.jpg&h=07b23d03&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9244007cd9bff3670da37da4515e9d54f9c10ce1","tid":533917,"uid":10726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T09:54:59.000Z","msg":"停花生"},{"pid":"3ca6c0b8976ba5a0fc909ee2f8b5f98990e7f332","tid":533917,"uid":39800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T09:55:00.000Z","msg":"粒水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cce7f1efa3b5ca3c3156f70e9f887b82fba0c1d8","tid":533917,"uid":48157,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T10:05: